NOTE: window and tabs both are considere same

- to switch to window/tab:
driver.switchTo().window(id/windowid/tabid);

- to close the window/tab
driver.close() -> current window
driver.quite() -> all windows

- to open new window: driver.switchTo().window(WindowType.WINDOW);
- to open new tab: driver.switchTo().window(WindowType.TAB);

- to get parent window/tab id:
String parentId = driver.getWindowHandle()

- to get all opened window/tab ids:
Set<String> allIds = driver.getWindowHandles();

- how to work with windows:
Set<String> allIds = driver.getWindowHandles();
for(String window : allIds){
  driver.switchTo().window(window);
  if(driver.getText().equals("yourvalue")){
    //do something
  }
}
NOTE:in if condition you can check pagetitle, pageurl, or something web element to confirm or shift to that tab
